title: Must do even it was so busy
text: This is the most busiest atttaction in Paris and there are some nice restaurants on it and the views were spectacular and this is the top must do in Paris

title: A Classic
text: My significant other and I drunkenly stumbled here a few weeks back. For a 'cliche' type experience it certainly was absolutely incredible. We popped in around 2200, and the Tower was beautifully lit. The view from the top is fantastic, but be prepared to dress warm. Definitely cold up there.

title: Wet weather
text: We had a tour to the Eiffel Tower while we were in Paris. Unfortunately one of the cable cars was down while there, which made the wait times a little longer even with skip the queue passes.
